<p><strong><span id="r-not.3">R-NOT.3<a class="headerlink" href="#r-not.3" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></strong> - Once a notification is successfully delivered, the Agent MUST reset the retry count to zero for the next notification Message.</p>

