<figcaption>Figure 26: Example of MTP Proxy in LAN with WAN Controller<a class="headerlink" href="#fig:example-of-mtp-proxy-in-lan-with-wan-controller" title="Permalink to this figure"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></figcaption>
